Thank you, that's a great help. That
many fewer should be no problem.

I'm sorry to ask again, but just
in case, could you escort the
soldiers to the Genbu Crown?

rows.label: qst105302_msg0001

That's a great help! It's much
easier to pass through now.

rows.label: qst105302_msg0002
rows.name:
We will advance the troops as
soon as we have gathered the
planned number of soldiers.

rows.label: qst105302_msg0003
rows.name:
It's embarrassing to say, but... due
to the recent commotion, we haven't
been able to secure enough soldiers.

rows.label: qst105302_msg0005
rows.name:
Then, could I ask you to escort
the soldiers to the Genbu Crown?

rows.label: qst105302_msg0101

Please escort the soldiers as
they head to the Genbu Crown.
